org.lafayette.server.http.digest
Class AuthorizationHeaderParser

java.lang.Object
  org.lafayette.server.http.digest.AuthorizationHeaderParser

public final class AuthorizationHeaderParser
extends Object

Parses the "Authorization" header field from a HTTP request. Header for digest authentication. 

 Authorization: Digest username="Foo",
                       realm="Private Area",
                       nonce="IrTfjizEdXmIdlwHwkDJx0",
                       httpMethod="GET",
                       uri="/",
                       response="$RESPONSE"

Sven Strittmatter
